API:
1. Implement simple api, that will accept Put/Get requests for small objects
    (less or equal to 4Gb), use SignatureV2 as example:

Canonical request
```
<HTTPMethod>\n // <------ Put Get Head
<CanonicalURI>\n // <------ Path to an object
<CanonicalHeaders>\n // <-------- x-date, Content-Type, AccessKey, Etag
```
Add to canonical request secret key (in first version it can be volume Id)
Use HMAC-sha256 - that is a signature, that will be put into Authorization header

Plans to expand functionality:
1. Implement users and user service that will manage users and their access to data
2. Split user service and management part, I guess that best practice is to 
    manage user access policies in different service